Vulois guides Child into the training room, where Windrazor is 
waiting.

"Windrazor, Child, it is time to begin your training. Now Windrazor, 
Child's training is going to be more advanced than yours, becaause he 
has been gifted. So let's...."

Comp:Temporal Annomily Detected!

Vulois: What?(Vulois runs out to the scanning room)On Screen.

A large picture of the Annomily appears.

"What is this?"

What do you think it is, Convix answered.

I...I don't know.

All I can tell you is to check it out. Take Windrazor and Child with 
you.

Vulois ran back to the training room.

"Looks like our first training is hands on! Follow me. If you can 
fly, than fly. If you can't, run as fast as you can. I'll try to keep 
it slow."

Vulois ran out of the embassy, went to Beast Mode, and taook off 
towards where the scanners had poined this thing out.
